Installation:

exec in console this command
git clone git://gitorious.org/rulinux-engine/ucaptcha.git UCaptcha

and move UCaptcha to your project

Than add to yuor code
require "path/to/Ucaptcha/UCaptcha.php";
where path/to/Ucaptcha is path to UCaptcha directory.

Installation in Symfony 2:

Add to deps file

[ucaptcha]
     git=git://gitorious.org/rulinux-engine/ucaptcha.git
     target=ucaptcha/lib/UCaptcha

and exec command

php bin/vendors install

Then add to autoload.php

$loader->registerNamespaces(array(
        //...
        'UCaptcha' => __DIR__.'/../vendor/ucaptcha/lib',
        //...
));

Thats all. UCaptcha now installed to your project

Using:

$captchaLevel = 1;//or other level
$uCaptcha = new UCaptcha\UCaptcha;
$uCaptcha->draw($captchaLevel);//returns path to image

after sending form your data

$uCaptcha->check($_POST['keystring']);
